             ®®®®®®®®®®®®®®®®|  ®®®®| ®®®®| @{" Future       " LINK FUTU}


      Welcome to LoTo98, a new lottery predictor and checker program,
      with features that include, a compact and well designed GUI and
      the ability to generate numbers using different methods.

      It can then be used to check these randomly generated numbers
      against those which have recently been drawn.

      In this version it has been improved in the following ways:

      · The GUI/window is now 5% smaller and hopefully looks better
      · Another random number generator has been created
      · A minor GUI based error caused by ACE basic has been fixed
      · Executable will be smaller and faster
      · Incompatibilities in high range Amiga are now sorted

@ENDNODE
